                Our current research focuses on developing and applying privacy-enhancing technologies to address trust challenges in data management, machine learning, and security. Key areas of exploration include <strong>Differential Privacy, Federated Learning, Trustworthy LLM/LLM, AI Security, Data Marketplaces</strong>, and beyond.
